data.meta_description: 10.1.1.462.745.pdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document discusses the software and software architecture for a student satellite called NUTS. It describes the requirements for an on-board computer module and highlights challenges with the current system design. It finds that existing software like the CubeSat Space Protocol and FreeRTOS can be used, but require some changes to work for this project. While existing software can save time, there are still many software challenges that need to be addressed.
